                                "component_media_credit": 'NIAID',
                                "component_media_caption": 'The style.scss file after adding the previous code.',
                                "component_media_lightbox": "yes"
                            }
                        %}

                        <p>You are now set up to use Font Awesome Pro with NDS. With Font Awesome Pro, you can access more Regular icons as well as the full set of Light and Duotone icons. If you would like more information on using Font Awesome with NPM, visit <a href="https://fontawesome.com/how-to-use/on-the-web/setup/using-package-managers">Font Awesome NPM Documentation</a>.</p>
